============================================================
				Vim Handy Reference
============================================================

the idea:
	action = [verb] + [noun]

all working vocab:
	operator
	motion
	text object
	selection

verb = operator
noun =
	motion 
	text object
		- inside or around a motion or selection
	parametrized text object
		- using f or t

